name: Nabbit
tag_list: cell-phones, technology, radio, music, tagging, downloading
overview:
Nabbit allows users tag songs and ads from the radio straight from their cell phones using text messaging and saves them in a personal Nabbit account. Nabbit is completely free.

In a Nabbit account users can create playlists, purchase songs from iTunes, Napster, Wal-Mart, and Amazon.com. Users can be connected to podcasts from their favorite talk radio segments. Users can search for concerts for that artist on Ticketmaster or TicketsNow. They can also download the ringtone and song lyrics.

If users click an ad that is enabled for Nabbit they can either purchase the product directly from the vendor’s website. Users may also be taken to an offer created just for Nabbit Users.

Nabbit has launched a Facebook application, and an iPhone application will be soon released.
